<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Bem-vindo ao nosso servi√ßo!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #333;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    strong {
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to our service!</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</p>
    <p>You have been successfully registered with our service. Below are your account details:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= @user.name %></li>
      <li><strong>E-mail:</strong> <%= @user.email %></li>
      <li><strong>CPF:</strong> <%= @user.cpf %></li>
      <li><strong>Admin:</strong> <%= @user.admin %></li>
      <li><strong>Company Name:</strong> <%= @user.company.name %></li>
      <li><strong>Company Phone:</strong> <%= @user.company.phone %></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Thanks for joining us!</p>
    <img src="https://static-cse.canva.com/blob/1387998/1600w-Fr4HcxPh4Z4.jpg" alt="MDN logo" width="565" />
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automatic email. Please don't respond.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
